{"tid":1009453,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"[筍盤?] 吳卓羲開全國首間figure博物館 包括價值$13萬1:1 Iron Man","createTime":"2019-02-05T07:46:39.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-06T08:22:55.000Z","uid":12558,"like":310,"dislike":24,"uniUserReply":72,"replies":[{"pid":"fe0ab19c1088dae2a0a87aff0c4135b58af2508a","tid":1009453,"uid":12558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T07:46:39.000Z","msg":"近年好少喺香港電視劇見到吳卓羲，原來佢最近喺北京開咗全國第一間figure博物館。<br />\n<br />\n呢個博物館名為《吳卓羲個人雕像模玩博物館》，展出咗佢收藏嘅超级英雄figure，包括Marvel、DC都有。<br />\n<br />\n之所以會選擇開博物館係因為兩個原因：第一，他收藏嘅figure數量實在太多，而每一個figure都要放喺可以完全欣賞到嘅地方，而佢屋企已經放唔落啦！<br />\n<br />\n第二，吳卓羲屋企養咗幾隻貓，主子好易整爛啲figure。<br />\n<br />\n而吳卓羲都對figure勁有興趣，想有一個地方俾其他figure狂熱份子交流，所以決定開呢個博物館。<br />\n<br />\n呢個博物館不設門票，展出咗吳卓羲大概三分之一嘅收藏品，另外仲有200幾個figure未運到。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/RkNMbwi.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRkNMbwi.png&h=4d8627cc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xjj6VX3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fxjj6VX3.png&h=b1c1e904&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/E51Ewwq.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FE51Ewwq.png&h=3f511553&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/L44R64N.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FL44R64N.png&h=99758743&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6uB5r49.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6uB5r49.png&h=426a3e4f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"842a03ff1d9918b65e211fa36e2766529e4088f1","tid":1009453,"uid":92697,"like":185,"dislike":25,"score":160,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-05T08:02:50.000Z","msg":"佢真係好靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n好想俾佢強姦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"21d01359226fd3923ff5ac6d6a4370e24eae9ef1","tid":1009453,"uid":89058,"like":230,"dislike":2,"s